                        "content": "Welcome to IntraVox",
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "**The modern intranet solution for Nextcloud.** Create beautiful, dynamic intranet pages with an intuitive drag-and-drop editor. No coding required."
