                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "What is IntraVox?",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "IntraVox transforms your Nextcloud into a powerful intranet platform. Build company portals, department pages, knowledge bases, and more - all within the secure environment of your Nextcloud server.\n\n**Key benefits:**\n\n- **Privacy-first** - Your data stays on your server\n- **No vendor lock-in** - Open source and self-hosted\n- **Seamless integration** - Works with existing Nextcloud users and groups\n- **Multi-language** - Built-in support for multiple languages"
                    }
                ]
